NOTES:

		* After the installation, Heritrix jobs directory
		 points to:
		/tmp/heritrix/jobs

		You can modify this behaviour in:
		/usr/lib/heritrix-$VERSION/conf/heritrix.properties

		* To start Heritrix, have a look on the start script:
		/etc/rc.d/heritrix

		* If you are behind a proxy, change the parameters, 
		"http-proxy-host" and "http-proxy-port" in the config file:
		/usr/lib/heritrix-$VERSION/conf/profiles/Simple/order.xml
